/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d29b6b2528d7073d21af41dfa5ff2297b69f12","tid":348432,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T16:46:45.000Z","msg":"但玩隨機視訊好多話我靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男同女都有<br />\n<br />\n岩岩試過 視像果時 人地睇嘅畫面都係掉轉"},{"pid":"7d5716d232ada7fd37025ee5efb8b5d515c1b61f","tid":348432,"uid":127075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T16:48:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>影相先係真樣<br />\n承認自己樣衰啦撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同FD行街經過商場果D落地玻璃望返佢都係唔多同樣</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n影相唔係真樣 因為係2D 有時光線角度都影響到 不過影相樣衰既話<br />\n通常都係樣衰 至於人同人身高對望角度都唔同 所以同真樣都有少少唔同"},{"pid":"aa7b0e662676a19dfe3340fdfc63a93a7cd8bc7b","tid":348432,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>影相先係真樣<br />\n承認自己樣衰啦撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同FD行街經過商場果D落地玻璃望返佢都係唔多同樣</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n影相唔係真樣 因為係2D 有時光線角度都影響到 不過影相樣衰既話<br />\n通常都係樣衰 至於人同人身高對望角度都唔同 所以同真樣都有少少唔同</blockquote><br />\n係 我都覺 定左格嘅自已左右掉轉果隻（別人眼中嘅你） 係樣衰d <br />\n<br />\n左右掉轉自已郁緊果隻 錄影 或 視像 都係靚仔"},{"pid":"f39cee5b2a14f1dc238af71dc37ae005de48d1fe","tid":348432,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T16:53:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"701ac2fcc89ccb41416e111c882d42dfc5f3720a","tid":348432,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T16:54:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇啲左右調返轉嘅鏡<br />\n從來都望唔到正面嘅自己咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 兩塊鏡拍埋 就會見到人地望到你個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1f12e2357646b75decfcef4dcf3545146fdffb","tid":348432,"uid":1870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T17:15:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquo